---
name: fab-hvac-strategy
description: Analyze fab CUS HVAC operating strategies and produce executable optimization plans with ROI and risk controls. Use when users ask for CUS strategy-package design, energy-saving estimation, medium/low-temperature loop optimization, heat-recovery coordination, abnormal-condition response, or policy recommendation reports.
---

# Fab Hvac Strategy

## Overview

Use this skill to evaluate and optimize fab CUS (medium-temperature + low-temperature + heat-recovery) operation with engineering constraints. Produce decisions that can be sent to plant operation teams: strategy package, expected savings, risk checks, and implementation priorities.

## Workflow

1. Confirm scope and plant constraints
2. Build load baseline and time-window split
3. Select candidate strategy packages
4. Quantify savings and uncertainty
5. Perform risk and feasibility checks
6. Output an execution-ready recommendation

